messages.text:
Hi there;

I see that you have signed the CLA in 2009 (perhaps for a non-Go
related issue), but you are not in the Go C+A files.

It's easier for us to just do this one-character change ourselves, but
if you want to be added, I'll do that. Let me know.
- gri
